response.overview: Filmed at the Paradise Rock Club in Boston, the hour is produced by Bill Burr of All Things Comedy. “The first time I saw Steph Tolev was a promotion video she made for a New York City show. I Immediately fell in love with her and her Comedy. One of the most uninhibited original voices out there today. I love everything about her!”
response.title: Steph Tolev: Filth Queen
